OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few light showers in the
OL,6,Fmorning which will soon fade away.
OL,7,FOtherwise a dry bright day with some
OL,8,Fsunny spells and lighter winds. High
OL,9,Fcloud thickening later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry but somewhat overcast in
OL,12,Fthe evening. It will remaining dry
OL,13,Fovernight with increasingly clear
OL,14,Fskies and freshening southeasterly
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FDry and bright morning with
OL,18,Fsome sunny spells. Chance of the odd
OL,19,Fshower around midday. Cloudier later
OL,20,Fwith strengthening southerly winds and
OL,21,Fthen rain in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
