OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FAny
OL,6,Fovernight rain soon clearing early
OL,7,FWednesday, then dry with bright spells
OL,8,Fand variable cloud before rain
OL,9,Fovernight. Sunny intervals and showers
OL,10,FThursday. Bright start Friday, wet and
OL,11,Fwindy later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
